    "description": "<p>OAKTREE CONSULTING</p>\n\n<p><strong>Oaktree </strong>is committed to providing quality and prompt services in the following areas</p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li>Permanent, contract and temporary recruitment for both local and foreign talents.</li>\n\t<li>Event/Project Recruitment</li>\n\t<li>Recruitment Process Outsourcing</li>\n\t<li>Payroll Outsourcing</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>Oaktree’s services cover every industry in the job market and we have a team of dedicated and industry-focused consultants in each of our three divisions.</p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li>Oaktree Technology</li>\n\t<li>Oaktree Engineering</li>\n\t<li>Oaktree Business Support </li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>We believe in ensuring every stage of our service process is professionally conducted and reviewing every resume submitted to ensure the candidate meet the right skills, qualifications and personality to perform to our client’s expectations.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n",
